  "message": "Update starlight-llms-txt to use asterisks for emphasis\n\nPicks up commit 2a1ae6d from our fork which configures remark-stringify\nto use asterisks instead of underscores for emphasis/strong markers.\nThis prevents unnecessary escaping of underscores in identifiers like\n`security_control`.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
